{"tid":1719942,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[攻略]最後文宣皇牌，Facebook戰線正式啟動!","createTime":"2019-11-14T08:05:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T02:41:38.000Z","uid":287028,"like":62,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"1ba9db607168e34a414f8af2dde266f3f37cf61d","tid":1719942,"uid":287028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T08:05:27.000Z","msg":"<strong><ins>前言</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n自6月抗爭運動以來，香港大眾主流資訊接收平台為(排名不分先後):<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">-Facebook<br />\n-電視媒體<br />\n-Youtube</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">-Whatsapp</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">-微信</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">-連登<br />\n-Telegram<br />\n-連儂牆</span><br />\n<br />\n截至 2019 年 1 月，香港約有 <span style=\"color: red;\">580 萬名活躍社交平台用戶</span>，佔整體人口 (746萬) 的 <span style=\"color: red;\">78%</span>。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QiioM1Q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQiioM1Q.png&h=a614d925&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Facebook為兵家必爭之地</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\nFacebook自6月起冒出大量內容農場Page及Group，每日餵養Followers， 甚至以Sponsor及Suggest形式強行出現在Timeline (基本上比錢就有)。 <span style=\"color: red;\">呢啲內容農場將事實扭曲，將影片圖片前後剪接加工，再配合虛假文字描述，惡意煽動及歪曲真相。</span>令好多接觸唔到真相嘅人信以為真。 加上大量海外水軍推波助瀾，令部份人錯信支持政權為社會主流。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>檢討以往打擊紅藍內容農場手法</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n手足們以往方法不外乎share link一齊檢舉及一齊洗版，但係Facebook平台上假Account及Fake news問題往往並沒有被重視。 加上<span style=\"color: red;\">對家內容農場以24hrs不眠不休，每3mins出一個post嘅速度去散播，業餘手足實在難以抗衡。</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>先了解Facebook Feeding Mechanism</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">每一個出現係你Timeline 嘅post其實都係經過Facebook精心篩選</span>，按照不同參數判斷乜野post應該出現係你Timeline。 以下為簡版運算邏輯:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LiEZ409.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLiEZ409.png&h=2d73e52a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我舉一個例子:<br />\n你每like一個黃post，佢就會出多兩個同類型嘅黃post比你; 你每like一個藍post佢又會比多兩個藍post比你。<br />\n<br />\n又或者你經常睇猫猫狗狗post，停留時間越長，佢之後就會出番更多猫猫狗狗post比你。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">換句話說，按照呢個運算邏輯，黃嘅人就會越黎越黃; 藍嘅人就會越黎越藍。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>咁係咪即係Facebook戰線好難打得贏?</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">非也。 就算內容農場幾用力發功，佢都會比一個重要參數所限制，就係上面 equation 嘅Creator 參數。</span> <br />\n[下刪一千字...]<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">簡單黎講就係滲透率。</span> 如果你Facebook朋友好多都係黃，咁你個facebook就會越黎越黃，藍post就會less likely出現係你Timeline。 好多內容農場都係呢幾個月先開始發功，一個新嘅Page/ Group要吸引一定數量觀眾係需要時間培養。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins>[*重點*]Facebook戰線應該點打?</ins></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n本來未去到最後我都唔想叫大家出大絕，但藍屍五毛滲透實在太強，而家唔開始反擊好快就會輸。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">與其去建立一個新嘅黃Page去抗衡對家，何不利用大家手上累積咗十幾年嘅資源? 無錯，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">就係你個account本身嘅人際網絡</span>。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">人人都是Facebook文宣。</span> <span style=\"color: orange;\">由呢一刻起將Facebook變成連登，變成telegram，將文宣同最update真相放係Facebook互相交流轉載。</span> <span style=\"color: red;\">試想想如果用100萬人嘅網絡去做文宣，擴散速度係可以幾何級上升。</span><br />\n<br />\n<ins>事前準備工夫:</ins><br />\n1. 防起底，更改個人account私隱設定為非公開。 特別係圖片。 具體點set自己逐項㩒入去研究，我唔詳解喇。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zqTj5kL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzqTj5kL.png&h=d4c15e71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2. 斷開Facebook 電話同多餘email連繫，防追蹤。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">3. 同連登一樣唔好係網上煽動違犯野，Popo會搵到你。 轉載 is welcome。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins>教學:</ins><br />\n1. 無需要unfriend藍屍，因為就係想佢地睇到文宣。<br />\n2. 文宣post要set做公開，朋友先可以轉發。<br />\n3. 識嘅朋友如果真係有心出賣你好容易，<span style=\"color: red;\">所以文宣應該以轉發share post及文宣圖為主，盡量避免以個人身份發表觸及法律底線之言論。</span><br />\n4. 多d將連登同tg 最新消息update去facebook，越新越突發先吸引到人去睇。<br />\n5. 同路朋友之間多啲互like，留言討論及轉發，增加post熱門度。<br />\n<br />\n多謝你耐心睇完個攻略，<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請立即行動加入戰線!!!<br />\n立刻!!!NOW!!!</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"d1b144e17e352a7a3e5a1b41e9de5d9a6413d881","tid":1719942,"uid":287028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T08:06:38.000Z","msg":"1個P牌推唔起"},{"pid":"e71c661a7f67648021bcbac9c884676077f2dd45","tid":1719942,"uid":104758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T08:06:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d257072be429e6260cdee94ce86f7f9510ea482","tid":1719942,"uid":287028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T08:06:49.000Z","msg":"2個P牌推唔起"},{"pid":"b1d9acb378d236503f95765bfef1b9c99e3d5fe3","tid":1719942,"uid":287028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T08:06:59.000Z","msg":"3個P牌推唔起"},{"pid":"712e17ac33ea794eedc19822d2c05054bb9f4235","tid":1719942,"uid":287028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T08:07:11.000Z","msg":"4個P牌推唔起"},{"pid":"0a36e80706c3d55f6d7309443fe2084b07cdd02b","tid":1719942,"uid":287028,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T08:07:23.000Z","msg":"5個P牌推唔起"},{"pid":"a61f47ca15d42368bb103e2d08b3f5b5db3c567e","tid":1719942,"uid":287028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T08:07:37.000Z","msg":"6個P牌推唔起"},{"pid":"8460513808a7551c287bd2f044866f5b683e3832","tid":1719942,"uid":287028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T08:07:47.000Z","msg":"7個P牌推唔起"},{"pid":"013093bcf1611b93d825ebc2f006ed95f30991e2","tid":1719942,"uid":65439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T08:07:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bf56b047ab1732bf22d3440eeff03515b610502","tid":1719942,"uid":287028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T08:08:00.000Z","msg":"8個P牌推唔起"},{"pid":"5d2494b7a26fb0cab0f1d64288e2d67334d018eb","tid":1719942,"uid":287028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi